14
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:22,599
let me give up,

15
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:25,040
and tell me you like him
and won't give anyone else a chance.

16
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,464
At least,

17
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,439
I won't do these stupid things anymore.

18
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,040
Then you should give up this idea now.

19
00:01:32,288 --> 00:01:37,376
♪Years go by and wind back again♪

20
00:01:39,008 --> 00:01:44,096
♪I take up the pen,
illustrating you in my memories♪

21
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,719
I don't need anyone.

22
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:48,000
Nor will I fall in love with anyone.

23
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,319
Whether it's you

24
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,319
or Mo Yunxi.

25
00:01:52,512 --> 00:01:54,464
♪Flowers by the Wangchuan River
haven't withered♪

26
00:01:55,027 --> 00:01:56,800
♪In my heart, they remain♪

27
00:01:58,899 --> 00:02:02,255
♪The fate of past and present
