35
00:02:22,816 --> 00:02:26,016
♪No longer fearing the future lives♪

36
00:02:26,016 --> 00:02:27,744
♪One more drink in the mortal world♪

37
00:02:27,744 --> 00:02:29,344
♪Just like we just met♪

38
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,599
Miss Ke,

39
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:32,000
I invited you here today

40
00:02:32,159 --> 00:02:33,560
(Serenity and far-reaching)
for Yunxi.

41
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:37,240
You know he has a lot on his mind.

42
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:40,960
From a young age he never tells
whatever is bothering him.

43
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,520
