45
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,000
Yunxi likes you.

46
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:52,000
Of course, I'm aware
that he has a weak constitution

47
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:54,360
and he's suffering
from a chronic illness.

48
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,159
No one knows

49
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,199
how long he can hold on.

50
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,439
He was born with this illness.

51
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:01,919
It's no one else's fault.

52
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:05,919
But I still hope he can find happiness.

53
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:09,039
(His illness wasn't given
by the heavens,)

54
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,360
(but me.)

55
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:12,919
(I caused it.)

56
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:20,400
(Miss Ke,)

57
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,479
