the betrothal gifts.)

58
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:25,719
(Yunxi had a big argument with me
after finding out.)

59
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:29,599
(He blamed me for making things difficult
for you without consulting him.)

60
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,360
(But...)

61
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:35,400
I'm just a father who feels
for his child.

62
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:38,759
