he can't say for himself,

63
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,680
so I have to say it for him.

64
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:42,960
Miss Ke,

65
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,439
I just hope

66
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:48,800
