77
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,439
Actually, I rarely dream.

78
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,319
But I have to thank Wangchuan Inn

79
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,800
for giving me a special experience.

80
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,879
If you hadn't unlocked my mental knots,

81
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,680
perhaps until I die,

82
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:33,399
I would still resent my parents
and my brother.

83
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,800
But your end
shouldn't have been like this.

84
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:58,759
Why do you always seem so unhappy?

85
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,399
I know,

86
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,639
to you,

87
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:08,600
perhaps I'm just a passerby.

88
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,519
But, Ke,

89
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:12,959
I hope you can be happy.

90
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,040
Rest assured and recuperate.

91
00:05:27,239 --> 00:05:28,319
You will definitely get better.

92
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:29,879
Trust me.

93
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:40,360
(In this life,)

94
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,120
(I must change his destiny.)

95
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,920
(I can't let him die before me.)

96
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,839
(This is all I can do.)

97
